name: Star Wars Art Print Ahsoka Tano 30 x 71 cm - unframed
description:
Sideshow presents the Star Wars: Ahsoka Tano™ Fine Art Print, an officially licensed Star Wars™ art print by artist Rich Davies.

Cunning and charismatic, the former Jedi Ahsoka Tano has captivated audiences since her first appearance in Star Wars animation. Now, this artwork honors her incredible legacy in live action. Standing in the burned forest of Corvus™ with a pale moon rising behind her, Ahsoka Tano ignites her twin Lightsabers™. This Togruta™ is resolute in her path to victory and justice, indicated by the elegant and unflinching expression on her face. Nothing and no one can stop her - though some may dare to try.

Inspired by the character's appearance in the Disney+ series Star Wars: The Mandalorian™, this Ahsoka Tano art is now available to fans as an unframed giclée print or in a custom framed presentation. Each Star Wars: Ahsoka Tano™ Fine Art Print features an embossed Sideshow Seal of Authenticity as part of the limited edition of 250 pieces. Pair it with the Ahsoka Tano Premium Format™ Figure by Sideshow - sold separately - for the ultimate tribute to this Force-wielding warrior.

There's always a bit of truth in legends. Bring home the Star Wars: Ahsoka Tano™ Fine Art Print by Rich Davies today!

Print details:

- Officially licensed by Lucasfilm
- Limited edition of 250
- 30 x 71 cm full bleed fine art giclée print
- Heavyweight 100% cotton, acid-free, certified archival Fine Art Paper
- Epson archival inks
- Embossed seal of authenticity
